values ('seed-release-date-nov-19', 'GTA 6 release date locked to 19 November 2026, reaffirmed on the Take-Two earnings call', 'Rockstar and Take-Two have held the 19 November 2026 launch date. It was reaffirmed on the 21 May earnings call and is baked into Take-Two full-year FY27 guidance of roughly 8 to 8.2 billion dollars. The game ships on PS5 and Xbox Series X and S, with no PC date given. This is the anchor fact every SixCentral countdown, guide and news piece should key off, and the strongest confirmed-over-rumour foundation you have.', '["Launch date 19 November 2026 on PS5 and Xbox Series X and S", "Reaffirmed on the 21 May 2026 Take-Two earnings call", "Baked into Take-Two FY27 guidance of about 8 to 8.2 billion dollars", "No PC release date given"]'::jsonb, 'Rockstar Games / Take-Two', 1, 12, '[{"outlet": "Variety", "url": "https://variety.com/2026/gaming/news/gta-5-no-delay-price-marketing-summer-1236755303/", "published_at": "2026-05-21T12:00:00Z"}, {"outlet": "TechTimes", "url": "https://www.techtimes.com/articles/317156/20260525/gta-6-release-date-locked-pre-orders-trailer-3-expected-late-june.htm", "published_at": "2026-05-25T12:00:00Z"}, {"outlet": "GamesRadar", "url": "https://www.gamesradar.com/gta-6-guide/", "published_at": "2026-05-22T12:00:00Z"}, {"outlet": "Wikipedia", "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grand_Theft_Auto_VI", "published_at": "2026-05-22T12:00:00Z"}]'::jsonb, true, 80.0, 53.6, 'confirmed', 'confirmed', 'run', 'new', '2026-05-21T12:00:00Z')
