values ('seed-trailer-3-window', 'Trailer 3 did not land with pre-orders, now widely expected mid-July around the World Cup final', 'Trailer 3 did not drop alongside pre-orders, which is now a confirmed non-event. Coverage across many outlets points to a mid-July window, with several tips clustering around the World Cup final on 19 July. As of early July nothing had been released. This is a live watch item, ideal for an evergreen updated when is Trailer 3 coming piece with a clear confirmed versus expected split.', '["Trailer 3 was not released with pre-orders", "Multiple outlets point to a mid-July window", "Several tips cluster around the World Cup final on 19 July", "Nothing released as of early July"]'::jsonb, 'GTA BOOM', 2, 12, '[{"outlet": "GTA BOOM", "url": "https://www.gtaboom.com/when-is-gta-6-trailer-3-coming-the-window-is-clearer-19a0", "published_at": "2026-07-02T12:00:00Z"}, {"outlet": "ComicBook", "url": "https://comicbook.com/gaming/news/gta-6-trailer-release-date-july/", "published_at": "2026-07-01T12:00:00Z"}, {"outlet": "Insider Gaming", "url": "https://insider-gaming.com/when-is-gta-6-trailer-3-releasing-june-2026-update/", "published_at": "2026-06-30T12:00:00Z"}, {"outlet": "VICE", "url": "https://www.vice.com/en/article/when-is-gta-6-trailer-3-releasing-rumored-date-hints/", "published_at": "2026-07-01T12:00:00Z"}, {"outlet": "Beebom", "url": "https://beebom.com/when-will-gta-6-trailer-3-come-out/", "published_at": "2026-07-01T12:00:00Z"}]'::jsonb, true, 67.0, 45.0, 'rumour', 'rumour', 'analysis', 'new', '2026-07-02T12:00:00Z')
